parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The maximum number of entries per page.

Valid values: 1 to 100.

Default value: 10.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The query token. Set the value to the `NextToken` value returned in the previous call to the DescribePrefixListAssociations operation. Leave this parameter empty the first time you call this operation.

parameters.name: PrefixListId
parameters.description: The ID of the prefix list.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the prefix list. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
